
'''''Drexciya'''''   ni filimi yo muri [[Gana]] yasohotse 2010 akaba documentary film ntoya  yayoboye na Akosua Adoma Owusu afatanije na California Institute wa Arts (CalArts)<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/535764-drexciya</ref><ref>http://www.africine.org/index.php/film/drexciya/18977</ref>. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu ikinamico mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam 2011 kandi yitabira ''Video ya Changing Same'' mu nzu ndangamurage ya Studio i Harlem, muri New York<ref>https://www.criterionchannel.com/videos/drexciya</ref> <ref>https://mcutimes.com/Movies/titles/291484/drexciya</ref>.

== Inyandiko ==
''Drexciya''   yerekana ikigo cyo koga rusange cyatawe giherereye i Accra, muri [[Gana]] cyashyizwe kuri Riviera. Riviera icyarimwe yari iterambere ridasanzwe<ref>https://alchetron.com/Drexciya-(film)</ref>, rigizwe nizamuka ryiza cyane hamwe na hoteri yinyenyeri eshanu. Kuva mu myaka ya za 70, Riviera yaguye mubihe bidasanzwe<ref>https://whitney.org/collection/works/44082</ref>. Iyi documentaire ngufi yahumetswe n imigani ya afro-futurist yakwirakwijwe nitsinda rya Drexciya ryitwa Detroit<ref>https://www.filmweb.pl/film/Drexciya-2010-633600/posters</ref>. Bavuga ko Drexciya ari umugani w’amazi utuwe n’abana bataravuka b’abagore b’abanyafrika bajugunywe mu nyanja mu gihe cy’ubucuruzi bw’abacakara ba Trans-Atlantike<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/259733921_Commentary_Haunting_in_Akosua_Adoma_Owusu's_Short_Experimental_Films</ref>. Aba bana bamenyereye kandi bahinduka kugirango bahumeke mumazi<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/black-film-the-future-weird-black-atlantis-akosua-owusu-drexciya-simon-rittmeier/</ref>.<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/akosua-adoma-owusu/</ref>

